steps.step: {"blocks":[{"key":"4tda1","text":"Download, save and unzip the Image Rating QC app from https://github.com/sbedford0/imageratingQCApp","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"UNDERLINE","offset":54,"length":45}],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":54,"length":45}],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"link","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"guid":"14398F88709011EDA1E10A58A9FEAC02","url":"https://github.com/sbedford0/imageratingQCApp"}}}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"b5oa9","text":"Follow the instructions in the “readme” file to run the program:","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"906se","text":"The first time you run the program, in a terminal, run ‘npm install’ in the app directory","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":1,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":56,"length":11}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"3l3sl","text":"Run ‘npm run build’ to build the app for production in the build folder and create a local version (you only need to do this once)","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":1,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":5,"length":13}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"eahp6","text":"Once you have done this, any time you want to start the app, run ‘npm run start’ in the app directory to launch the app in a web browser","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":1,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":66,"length":13}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"abc96","text":"Click ‘browse’ to select and load in your images and start rating! ","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":1,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"4hoko","text":"Note: if you have a large dataset, try to limit yourself to maximum ~2000 subjects in one session to avoid fatigue and distraction","type":"unstyled","depth":1,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":0,"length":4}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"d6j8u","text":"Rate by either clicking the buttons or using arrow keys ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"148v9","text":"Thumbs down (← key):       BAD","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":27,"length":3}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"7dk2m","text":"Shrug (↓ key):                     MINOR ERROR ","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":35,"length":12}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"33tsb","text":"Thumbs up (→ key):            GOOD","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":30,"length":4}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"66pdv","text":"Brain with ripples (↑ key):  VISIBLE MOTION / POOR SCAN QUALITY","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":29,"length":34}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"66irk","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"ck7d1","text":"See Guidelines for rating criteria, and Materials for examples of outputs and ratings","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"29lrr","text":"When you have gone through all of the images, a download button will appear. Click this to download your ratings as a csv file.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
